{"tid":2161972,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：中國駐英絕交官  劉曉明自閉式反制羅傑斯（李八方）","createTime":"2020-08-18T01:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T01:58:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4eb2eac751a4fa41adaffef8d6f14051fc2cf309","tid":2161972,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T01:10:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200818/ACSHLL5JARALHOBBESUEECMUSM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200818%2FACSHLL5JARALHOBBESUEECMUSM%2F&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21Mtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=d6af0f94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200818%2FACSHLL5JARALHOBBESUEECMUSM%2F&h=e6ac0f2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200818/ACSHLL5JARALHOBBESUEECMUSM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：中國駐英絕交官 <br />\n劉曉明自閉式反制羅傑斯（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EJYhgaVVkkgv-6grbVIdKFBBnDU=/1081x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AUB5SCC54NGENKMULAOOKJRLQ4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEJYhgaVVkkgv-6grbVIdKFBBnDU%3D%2F1081x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAUB5SCC54NGENKMULAOOKJRLQ4.JPG&h=0131f76d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■經常tag劉曉明嘅羅傑斯，發現最近Twitter賬戶被對方封鎖。<br />\n<br />\n中國式「戰狼外交」一向惹笑，西方政界不時喺Twitter恥笑戰狼外交官，英國民間組織Hong Kong Watch發起人羅傑斯係其中一個。佢經常tag中國駐英國大使劉曉明，質問佢新疆同香港人權問題。劉曉明最近搵到反制武器，就係「自閉式襲擊」block user，直接封鎖羅傑斯Twitter賬戶。堂堂外交官變「絕交官」，有連登仔不禁問：「這是正式錄用的外交官嗎？」不過羅傑斯喺分享連登仔呢個討論時，無端端畀網民話佢犯咗禁都唔知。<br />\n<br />\n羅傑斯轉發連登粗口po<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MEEc8faJ7HVwmAL6ecK3zTaBho8=/8404x5728/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/52LWIOMG5VE6NOETCRRVCJHE3I.GIF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMEEc8faJ7HVwmAL6ecK3zTaBho8%3D%2F8404x5728%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F52LWIOMG5VE6NOETCRRVCJHE3I.GIF&h=f6ec990c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n羅傑斯Twitter出po，話劉曉明喺Twitter賬戶block咗佢，仲喺個人Twitter貼文分析「死因」。原來羅傑斯最近頻頻tag劉曉明，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n羅傑斯俾劉曉明block呢單嘢，連登仔好快開po恥笑，仲笑劉曉明「這是正式錄用的外交官嗎？」羅傑斯好快將連登討論區恥笑「絕交官」嘅po喺Twitter分享，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n李八方"},{"pid":"aae0be5d18030f2da54a260176691edcee983f75","tid":2161972,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T01:13:25.000Z","msg":"有中國特色的外交手段<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb11c6de1c118754ea9ea53e7bd21578e4041ed","tid":2161972,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T01:22:10.000Z","msg":"叫掘窿外交貼切過戰狼外交啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n掘個窿埋自己個頭落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db51d5dd4ded3c4ab12382ad539bade8ee0afd31","tid":2161972,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T01:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a8a4ffbd16a33227f8d5192eba865a2ce685d27","tid":2161972,"uid":68556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T01:58:34.000Z","msg":"自絕於網民  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}